1. Ja sam *unajmio* stan u centru grada. (I rented an apartment in the city center.)
2. On je *unajmio* automobil za putovanje. (He rented a car for the trip.)
3. Ona je već mesecima *unajmila* kuću na obali mora. (She has been renting a house on the seaside for months.)
4. Mi smo *unajmili* poslovni prostor u novom tržnom centru. (We rented office space in a new shopping center.)
5. Oni su juče *unajmili* kamion za selidbu. (They rented a truck for the move yesterday.)
6. Kada su *unajmili* stan, morali su da ostave depozit. (When they rented the apartment, they had to leave a deposit.)
7. *Unajmio* sam majstora da popravi krov. (I hired a handyman to fix the roof.)
8. Oni su *unajmili* profesionalnog kuvara za svoju restoran. (They hired a professional chef for their restaurant.)
9. Njihova firma je nedavno *unajmila* novog direktora. (Their company recently hired a new director.)
10. *Unajmili* su studente da rade kao promoteri na sajmu. (They hired students to work as promoters at the fair.)